data.description: Your Favorite Master Suite!!!! Fantastic home in Claremont Ranch. Freshly Painted with a New Roof! New Black Trim Paint to be completed on October 22! This home has been lovingly cared for and several upgrades initiated. Main-level upgrades include a built-in fireplace with shelves around. Pre-wired surround sound. Walk-out to the Deck with Views! The Kitchen has updated counters and cabinets plus a nice Pantry. Upstairs there are 2 additional bedrooms and a bath. Then walk through the double doors into the best Master Suite around! HUGE! Plenty of room for your furniture and a sitting are as well. 5 Piece Bath plus an oversized Walk-in Closet. The Basement finish has been started to include a 1/2 bath and Laundry Room. A Second Family room has been framed in as well. The back yard has a perfect patio ready for your fire pit. Don't miss this one!
